      <title>中国将打破全国人大总理新闻发布会的传统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-premier-li-will-not-hold-press-conference-at-npc-breaking-from-tradition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李强不会在全国人民代表大会结束时举行新闻发布会，这打破了长期以来的政治传统，并加剧了人们对信息获取渠道减少的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-premier-li-will-not-hold-press-conference-at-npc-breaking-from-tradition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:54:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超级星期二即将到来，海莉在华盛顿特区初选首次获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/haley-gets-first-primary-win-in-d-c-with-super-tuesday-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[妮基·黑莉 (Nikki Haley) 周日在哥伦比亚特区赢得共和党初选，这让她在 2024 年提名竞赛中取得首场胜利，并减缓了唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 获得共和党提名的进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/haley-gets-first-primary-win-in-d-c-with-super-tuesday-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美韩开始军事演习激怒金正恩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-south-korea-start-military-drills-set-to-anger-kim-jong-un</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和韩国开始了最大规模的年度联合军事演习之一，此举肯定会激怒朝鲜，朝鲜在年初就威胁要摧毁其南部邻国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-south-korea-start-military-drills-set-to-anger-kim-jong-un</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:05:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥候选人谢因鲍姆表示养老金没有面临危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/mexico-candidate-sheinbaum-says-pensions-aren-t-in-danger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统竞选领先者克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆表示，她的政府不会面临养老金消失或改变的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/mexico-candidate-sheinbaum-says-pensions-aren-t-in-danger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 01:40:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将采取法律措施惩罚罢工医生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/south-korea-to-start-legal-steps-to-punish-doctors-in-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国计划启动法律程序，可能会导致对因抗议增加医学院入学率计划而辞职并扰乱医疗保健的医生进行惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/south-korea-to-start-legal-steps-to-punish-doctors-in-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反抗习近平的香港年轻人现在在中国参加派对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-03/young-hong-kongers-who-defied-xi-are-now-partying-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[创纪录数量的居民涌入深圳寻求廉价食品和美好时光，加速了一度被城市热爱自由的年轻人拒绝的融合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-03/young-hong-kongers-who-defied-xi-are-now-partying-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯呼吁加沙停火并释放以色列人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/harris-calls-for-gaza-cease-fire-release-of-israeli-hostages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯呼吁以色列和哈马斯之间暂时停火，因为有关释放 10 月 7 日袭击中被劫持人质的协议的谈判仍在拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/harris-calls-for-gaza-cease-fire-release-of-israeli-hostages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 22:59:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特宣布为预算增长提供英国制造业资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/hunt-announces-uk-manufacturing-funding-in-budget-growth-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特在周三公布预算之前宣布提供新资金支持英国制造业，他表示预算将侧重于长期增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/hunt-announces-uk-manufacturing-funding-in-budget-growth-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚与东南亚在中国阴影下加强联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/australia-southeast-asia-push-to-bolster-ties-in-china-s-shadow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不久前，东南亚还认为澳大利亚的外交政策与美国的外交政策过于紧密。但本周在墨尔本举行的地区领导人聚会表明堪培拉希望开辟自己的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/australia-southeast-asia-push-to-bolster-ties-in-china-s-shadow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦选择谢巴兹·谢里夫连任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/pakistan-set-to-elect-shehbaz-sharif-as-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两个保守派政党组成联盟以阻止被监禁的政治家伊姆兰·汗的政党失去权力后，谢巴兹·谢里夫被选为巴基斯坦总理，连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/pakistan-set-to-elect-shehbaz-sharif-as-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 03:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
